h3. Summary

Getting {{Failed to retrieve favorite filters from server}} message on _Issue Navigator_ when  one of the filters is shared with a deleted group.
The endpoint _/rest/api/2/filter/favourite/_ and the filter endpoint _/rest/api/2/filter/<filter_id>?expand_ returns {noformat}
{"errorMessages":["Internal server error"],"errors":{}}
{noformat}
Also getting: popup message if the dashboard uses the Favourite filters

h3. Steps to reproduce
# Create a test group and have a user in it
# Create a test filter (it will be added as favourite automatically)
# Go to _Manage Filter_ and share that filter with test group
# Delete the test group
# Open the test filter or go to Issue Navigator

h3. Current Result
The _Favorite Filters_ are not displayed and the drop down menu is gone.
- !image-2015-12-30-18-56-02-118.png|thumbnail!

h3. Expected Result
The _Favorite Filters_ and the drop down menu are displayed. 

h3. Workaround
Remove the deleted group from the filter (_Manage Filter -> select the affected fitler -> Edit -> Remove the group_)

